{"tid":2051539,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《RAC1》稱，美斯硬撼巴塞主席！帶隊友拒絕二次減薪","createTime":"2020-06-05T00:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:02:09.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3adafebe62d359ac6317a39967ec5bc9810e784a","tid":2051539,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"美斯（Lionel Messi）等球員拒絕了巴塞隆拿球會第二輪降薪的要求，雙方的關係可能再度變得緊張起來。<br />\n<br />\n  《RAC1》稱，球會主席貝圖美奧（Josep Bartomeu）在5月底的訓練中向美斯等人提出了第二輪降薪的想法，希望他們能再放棄一些收入，但這一次，美斯和球員們強硬的予以了拒絕，雙方不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n  在三月份時，美斯和隊友們已經同意了第一輪降薪方案，據悉為巴塞球會節省了1500萬歐元，但目前巴塞仍希望再靠降薪節省1000萬歐元，這遭到了球員們的拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n  6月13日，巴塞將對陣馬略卡，球員們認為，既然已經恢復工作，就沒有理由再接受降薪。"},{"pid":"4813c179723d36fc14565edf9adeeafe11a23d27","tid":2051539,"uid":112232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"邊個話美欺冇領導能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d8b38e646e12abad44042b4525afd2b679cb4","tid":2051539,"uid":88654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:58:16.000Z","msg":"拒絕溫室的小花 抗爭到底"},{"pid":"09f750479dc4b1dd46916f398c2a3c1846e7bea1","tid":2051539,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"我要與你硬碰"},{"pid":"a88c155359c3e8f930fab28fb85a98661e7c2c25","tid":2051539,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1586f35542406a934470d07fbdac3cd863205a52","tid":2051539,"uid":99725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"又減人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴塞有冇咁唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos